Additionally, the paper mentions the use of an iterative method for keypoint estimation and pose prediction, which suggests that it may also belong to the Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI) category. The paper also deals with the problem of 3D pose estimation, which may make it relevant to the Multimedia (cs.MM) category. Finally, the paper discusses the training of Deep Convolutional Neural Networks, which may make it relevant to the Neural and Evolutionary Computing (cs.NE) category.
